STEPS TO GET THE AUDIO RECORDER WORKING PROPERLY WITH DEPENDENCIES

Install the Port audio dependency from http://www.portaudio.com/download.html

Extract it
./configure
make

sudo make install

sudo apt-get install libsndfile1

g++ -o audio_recorder record_audio.cpp -lportaudio -lsndfile -lm -lsndfile

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev

Run the audio recorder to your hearts desire